# Internationalization (i18n)

- **No hardcoded UI copy** in components — use message catalogs (`next-intl`, `react-intl`, or project standard).
- **Routing:** locale prefix (`app/[locale]/...`) or agreed strategy; middleware for detection only as in existing codebase.
- **Formatting:** `Intl.NumberFormat`, `Intl.DateTimeFormat`, `Intl.RelativeTimeFormat`, `Intl.DisplayNames` — never manual date/number concatenation for display.
- **Pluralization:** use ICU / library plural rules — do not concatenate “count + word” in English-only order.
- **Fallback:** default locale when a key is missing; log missing keys in dev.
- **SEO:** `hreflang` / canonical per project SEO rules.
- **RTL:** layout/mirroring when Arabic/Hebrew/etc. are in scope.
